      <title>美国寻求盟友帮助遏制中国人工智能芯片发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-to-seek-curbs-on-asml-tokyo-electron-support-for-china-s-ai-memory-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国高级官员即将访问日本和荷兰，要求两国对中国半导体行业增加新的限制，包括其生产人工智能所需的高端存储芯片的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-to-seek-curbs-on-asml-tokyo-electron-support-for-china-s-ai-memory-chips</guid>
